sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Login Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant Auth as Auth Guard
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open login page
    UI->>LW: mount()
    LW->>Auth: Check existing authenticated user
    alt Already logged in
        Auth-->>LW: Authenticated
        LW-->>UI: Redirect to portal home
    else Not logged in
        Auth-->>LW: Guest
        LW-->>UI: Render login form
    end

    User->>UI: Submit username and password
    UI->>LW: login()
    LW->>LW: Validate required fields
    LW->>Auth: attempt(credentials)
    alt Success
        Auth->>DB: Verify credentials
        DB-->>Auth: Valid user
        Auth-->>LW: Authenticated
        LW-->>UI: Regenerate session + redirect intended page
    else Failed
        Auth->>DB: Verify credentials
        DB-->>Auth: Invalid credentials
        Auth-->>LW: Failed
        LW-->>UI: Show username/password error messages
    end
